    "Html": "\r\n<div id=\"x__mcePaste\" style=\"width:1px; height:1px; overflow:hidden; top:0px; left:-10000px\">\r\n&#65279;</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">My Development environment:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">VS2010 Ultimate</span></span></div>\r\n</li><li>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Microsoft SQL Server 2008 R2</span></span></div>\r\n</li><li>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">MVC Music Store Tutorial v2.0</span></span></div>\r\n</li></ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">Issue found while Testing the Client-Side Validation pg. 91</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">I was having no issues with this tutorial until testing the client-side validation. For some reason the validation rules worked but the red css coloring didn&rsquo;t work. I finally\r\n found an issue with the MvcMusicStore\\MvcMusicStore\\Content\\themes\\base\\<strong>jquery-ui.css</strong> file.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">When I tried to open the file in VS, I received this pop-up:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">Inconsistent Line Endings</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">The line endings in the following file are not consistent. Do you want to normalize the line endings?\r\n</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">I clicked yes, and now everything works as designed. I hope this helps someone else.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">BTW, a BIG thx to all that brought us MVC 3, !</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:small\">Brian</span></p>\r\n",
